            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著市場對輕鬆騎行的需求不斷增長，電動輔助自行車的普及度也逐漸上升。不過，電動自行車需要依賴充電，且電池與馬達的使用壽命有限。為了應對這些問題，日本汽車部件製造商推出了一項不需要電力驅動、僅依靠彈簧原理來減輕騎行負擔的新技術。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda041screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304285" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda041screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda041screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda041screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda010screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda010screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda010screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda010screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda013screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304274" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda013screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda013screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda013screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>這項名為「Reloda」的技術，其靈感來自汽車離合器中的阻尼器。其基本運作方式是，當騎行者踩下腳踏板時，大盤中的彈簧會被壓縮，然後彈簧反彈的力量會推動腳踏板，從而減輕腳部的施力。根據日本神户大學的研究，這項技術能有效減少約 20% 的肌肉負擔，讓騎行者能夠輕鬆完成長時間騎行。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113389-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113389-1-694x455.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113389-1-694x455.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113389-1.jpg 915w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113390.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304281" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113390.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="426" /></a></p><p>該技術的運作過程也極為簡單，當腳踏板被踩下時，彈簧會進行壓縮，並儲存能量。隨著腳踏板的回彈，彈簧會釋放這些儲存的能量，並有效推動腳踏板前進。這樣的設計使得騎行者在踩踏過程中所需的力量大大減少，從而減輕了肌肉的疲勞。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda155screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda155screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda155screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda155screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>「Reloda」技術的核心是模擬汽車離合器中的減震器，這一創新不僅解決了電動輔助自行車的充電問題，還能幫助使用者提高騎行效率，無論是長時間的平地騎行還是爬坡，都能減少肌肉負擔。這項技術的研發不僅代表著汽車零部件技術在自行車領域的應用，也顯示出彈簧技術在未來可能的廣泛應用。</p><p>在神户大學的研究中，實驗顯示，使用這項技術的自行車相比傳統車型能顯著減少人體的肌肉負擔。研究表明，當騎行者佩戴 Reloda 系統時，腳部所需施加的力量減少了 20%，這一數據對於長途騎行者來説，無疑是一大福音。這項技術的出現不僅讓騎行變得更輕鬆，還能提高整體騎行體驗，進一步吸引了那些長時間騎行的消費者。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113393-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113393-1-647x580.jpg" alt="" width="647" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113393-1-647x580.jpg 647w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/113393-1.jpg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 647px" /></a></p><p>以下是每個旋轉角度的詳細解釋，説明 Reloda 技術在每個階段如何減輕騎行者的肌肉負擔：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda118screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304264" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda118screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda118screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda118screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲0 度：當腳踏板在起始位置，即剛開始踩踏時，彈簧開始受到壓縮。此時，彈簧儲存能量，準備在接下來的過程中釋放，幫助腳踏板向下移動。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda122screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda122screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda122screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda122screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲45 度：當騎行者的腳開始踩下踏板時，彈簧繼續壓縮。這時候，彈簧的力量開始提供支持，減少了腳部需要施加的力量。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda126screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda126screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda126screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda126screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲90 度：在這個角度，彈簧處於接近最大壓縮狀態，為騎行者提供最大的支持，並減少了肌肉負擔，特別是對於下壓踏板的時候。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda130screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda130screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda130screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda130screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲135 度：此時，彈簧開始釋放儲存的能量，並繼續向外伸展，幫助腳踏板向前進行轉動。騎行者的肌肉負擔再次減少，並進一步支持下個踏板移動。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda135screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda135screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda135screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda135screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲180 度：當腳踏板達到半圈的位置時，彈簧基本上已經完成了最大的壓縮並開始向外反彈，進一步幫助推動踏板，使腳步更輕鬆。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda139screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda139screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda139screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda139screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲225 度：當踏板接近後半圈時，彈簧繼續伸展並提供反向支持，減少騎行者在這一階段所需的肌肉力量，幫助完成踏板的轉動。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda143screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda143screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda143screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda143screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲270 度：這時彈簧接近完全伸展，對騎行者的支持達到最大，幫助騎行者維持穩定的力量輸出，減少肌肉的過度使用。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda148screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304271" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda148screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda148screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda148screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲315 度：踏板接近一圈的結束，彈簧的反彈動作繼續協助腳踏板進行旋轉，這有助於進入下一個踏板循環，減少每次踩踏所需的力量。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda153screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304272" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda153screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda153screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda153screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><br />
▲360 度：當踏板完成一圈後，彈簧的能量基本上已經完全釋放並準備重新壓縮。此時，騎行者的肌肉負擔減少，並準備開始新的踏板循環。</p><p>總結來説，Reloda 技術通過彈簧在不同角度的壓縮和反彈來輔助騎行者，在踩踏過程中逐步提供支援，減少肌肉的使用，從而提高騎行效率，特別是在長時間和高強度的騎行中能夠顯著減輕疲勞。</p><p>目前，這項技術的專利已經申請成功，並且正在向市場推廣。雖然目前的測試結果顯示它在減輕肌肉負擔方面已經取得了不小的成效，但未來仍有進一步改良的空間，特別是在如何進一步優化彈簧設計和提高其耐用性方面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda231screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda231screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda231screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/reloda231screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>隨著這項技術的應用，未來我們或許能見到更多無需電池和充電的輕鬆騎行體驗，這無疑將對自行車市場產生深遠影響。至於未來，Reloda 技術是否能成為新一代騎行裝置的標配，還需要時間來驗證。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_63274"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PalU7iluEFE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://carcareplus.jp/article/2025/04/20/11346.html">Carcareplus</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/20/reloda/life-tech/bike/">毋須用電，只用彈簧減輕騎單車負擔，日本新技術 Reloda 省力最高達 20%</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
